                                        <hr>
                                          <strong>  How to Apply:</strong>
                                            </h2>
<p>

<pre>
Step 1: click on link to start the registration process.
Step 2: You will receive an activation email, once you have completed the registration process.
Step 3: Click on the activation link to register successfully and then login your account.
Step 4: Select the applicable scholarship according to your state.
Step 5: Fill in the required details and upload the required documents.
Step 6: Submit to complete the application process. 

</pre>

